ing: 2 cups baby spinach leaves, or to taste
1 carrot, peeled and cut into large chunks
3/4 cup plain fat-free Greek yogurt, or to taste
des: "Easy and simple, you'll have this smoothie in no time. This smoothie is packed with nutrients and vitamins. It's also perfect if you're in a hurry to get to work, rushing your kids to school (rushing yourself to school...like me), or just craving a fresh and healthy drink to start your day. Organic maple syrup can be added instead of honey."
ins: Put spinach, banana, carrot, yogurt, ice, and honey in a blender; blend until smooth.
